---
---
<section id="about">
  <div class="section-header reveal">
    <span class="sec-num">01</span>
    <h2 class="sec-title">About</h2>
    <div class="sec-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <p>
        I'm an <strong>IT Support Supervisor</strong> based in Bali, Indonesia, with over five years of hands-on experience managing enterprise-level IT infrastructure at ICS Travel Group.
      </p>
      <p>
        My work spans network architecture, server administration, team leadership, and vendor coordination. Keeping systems stable for a distributed, multi-location travel company.
      </p>
      <blockquote>
        I build websites the same way I build infrastructure. With performance, reliability, and the real user in mind.
      </blockquote>
      <p>
        Currently seeking <strong>freelance web projects</strong>, particularly for small businesses and local brands that need a professional online presence without the enterprise price tag.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-aside reveal">
      <div class="aside-block">
        <span class="mono-label">Education</span>
        <p class="aside-val">Diploma in Information Engineering</p>
        <p class="aside-sub">NewMedia College · Sep 2016</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-block">
        <span class="mono-label">Location</span>
        <p class="aside-val">Bali, Indonesia</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-block">
        <span class="mono-label">Languages</span>
        <p class="aside-val">Bahasa Indonesia (native)</p>
        <p class="aside-val">English (conversational)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-block">
        <span class="mono-label">Looking for</span>
        <p class="aside-val">Freelance web work, collaborations, part-time dev roles</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
#about {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 120px 56px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.section-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 64px;
}
.sec-num {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--accent-red);
}
.sec-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}
.sec-line {
  flex: 1;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--border);
}

.about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
  gap: 80px;
  align-items: start;
}

.about-text p {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  line-height: 1.85;
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.about-text p strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }

blockquote {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--ink);
  padding: 0 0 0 24px;
  margin: 36px 0;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.about-aside {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0;
}

.aside-block {
  padding: 20px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.aside-block:first-child { padding-top: 0; }

.mono-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink-faint);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.aside-val {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--ink);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.aside-sub {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--ink-dim);
  margin-top: 2px;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  #about { padding: 80px 24px; }
  .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
}
</style>
